lead_paragraph: Celina Rodrigo scored 12 points to help No. 6 Texas defeat No. 22 West Virginia 67-51 in a Big 12 women's tournament semifinal.

headline.print_headline: No. 6 Texas Tops No. 22 West Virginia, Moves to Big 12 Final
